      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "AGENT TWENTY ONE (7) is a well performed dog and winner of nine races who is worth forgiving after finishing out of the placings at this track (31.17). Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings three times from five attempts. Has ability and looks hard to stop. PROTEGE (8) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing eighth (31.64) in a Special conditions race at this track. Warrants plenty of respect. WHITE HAWKE (1) carved over from wide out and boxed on strongly to finish 1.75 lengths away in second (19.84) behind CATCH MY DESIGN at this track. Goes well out of this box with a win and five minor placings. Leading player again. CATCH MY DESIGN (4) was a shock winner last start and can measure up again.",
